    net.milkbowl.vault2.economy.Economy.createAccount(UUID, String)
    This method is deprecated as of version 2.8, and has been replaced by Economy.createAccount(UUID, String, String, boolean). This allows economy plugins to know exactly if the account is a player or not. This may be removed in a future release.
